    {
      "title": "TraceQL Queries & Key Attributes",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 52 },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Explore Queries (Explore → Tempo)\n\n| Query | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| `{ span.gen_ai.usage.cache_read.input_tokens > 0 }` | Cache hits |\n| `{ span.gen_ai.usage.cache_creation.input_tokens > 0 }` | Cache misses |\n| `{ span.gen_ai.operation.name = \"chat\" } \\| count_over_time() by (span.gen_ai.request.model)` | Calls by model |\n| `{ span.gen_ai.operation.name = \"execute_tool\" } \\| avg(duration) by (span.gen_ai.tool.name)` | Tool latency |\n| `{ status = error && resource.service.name = \"copilot-chat\" }` | Errors |\n\n## Key Attributes\n\n| Attribute | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `gen_ai.usage.cache_read.input_tokens` | Tokens from cache (hit) |\n| `gen_ai.usage.cache_creation.input_tokens` | Tokens cached (miss) |\n| `gen_ai.usage.input_tokens` | Total input tokens |\n| `gen_ai.usage.output_tokens` | Output tokens |\n| `gen_ai.request.model` | Model name |\n| `gen_ai.tool.name` | Tool invoked |\n| `gen_ai.agent.name` | Agent name |\n| `copilot_chat.time_to_first_token` | TTFT (ms) |"
      }
    }
